Michael Marillier with Bafana Bafana's Dean Furman as part of eNCA's 12 Days of Crazy. JOHANNESBURG - On day 3 of eNCA's 12 Days of Crazy, Michael Marillier played a penalty shootout with Bafana Bafana's Dean Furman. Watch the video below.  Michael Marillier spent the morning with Bafana Bafana Captain Dean Furman. Watch the video to see if Michael managed to stop the ball before it hit the net.